o locale, et gardez une marge horaire entre chaque visite pour absorber les imprévus. Mon conseil : À l''Aman New York (Crown Building), les suites ''Upper Crown'' aux étages 24-26 disposent d''une vue dégagée sur Central Park au nord — éviter les suites des étages 18-20 dont la vue est partiellement obstruée par les immeubles voisins. Anticipez les créneaux les moins fréquentés sur les sites incontournables de New York — Broadway & soirée finale — souvent tôt le matin ou en fin d''après-midi juste avant la fermeture.","body_en":"Nuit Broadway — The Mark Jean-Georges déjeuner, shopping SoHo ou Nolita, spectacle Broadway prémunicipalement réservé (Book of Mormon, Hamilton option), champagne bar Aman New York rooftop. Area: New York — Broadway & soirée finale. Key stops: Broadway (Theater District), Times Square, Radio City Music Hall, Lincoln Center. Pick a centrally located hotel in New York — Broadway & soirée finale to keep transfer time low and free up the most experience-rich hours. Wear comfortable shoes adapted to local weather, and keep a fifteen-minute buffer between stops to absorb the unexpected — a slow check-in, a longer queue, a chance encounter worth pausing for. Time your visits to the marquee sites in New York — Broadway & soirée finale for the least crowded windows — usually early morning or the last hour before closing. Book starred lunches at least three weeks ahead in shoulder season; top chefs cap covers deliberately and refuse late requests during peak weeks.","hotel_id":null,"duration_days":1,"city":"New York — Broadway & soirée finale","poi":["Broadway (Theater District)","Times Square","Radio City Music Hall","Lincoln Center"]}]'::jsonb,
